{"id":"02ede44b-39fc-4999-be56-42163adaeb8b","name":"SCP-1471 (Malo) - The Anomaly","description":"<h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 131, 75)\">\"Y'know, people keep saying I should get my suit refitted. What do you think?\"</span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2dbd012d-9877-40e5-9418-fd8f2ea55513_5711bc9f-7db8-4a7d-9cb5-7ea7f0d3adeb.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 521px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p>Okay, here's this beaut. Everyone's done Malo at least once, right? Figured I'd throw my hat in the ring. Anyways, major thanks to <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/1102058e-f34b-47d4-ba54-b3456ddf7c51_profile-of-sannoji\" target=\"_blank\">Sannoji </a>for both the usual help and additional help on an idea for this little creature. Next up, I'll be returning to form with the classic trope; a fuckin' femboy! So hopefully you'll stick around till then, cuz that'll be a doozy!</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2dbd012d-9877-40e5-9418-fd8f2ea55513_c7aa4aee-5bf1-4543-b0c5-05883f9943cd.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 268px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p>Art by: <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://e621.net/posts/4336723?q=scp-1471+inu-sama\" target=\"_blank\">inu_sama</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"2dbd012d-9877-40e5-9418-fd8f2ea55513_5cbf3cd4-d038-459b-b12b-47fc4bac717f.webp","creator":"posadaspam","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🦄 Non-human","👧 Monster Girl","🐺 Furry"],"chats":3452,"messages":21521,"created_at":"2024-08-19T08:01:48.423060+00:00"}